Description: Rational Energies transforms waste into energy.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Minneapolis-Saint Paul Area, Great Lakes, Midwestern US
Full Description: Rational Energies transforms something nobody wants – waste – into something everybody wants – energy. Today their advanced oil process converts used motor oil into lubricant blend stocks and fuels that meet industry standards for quality and consistency. They are developing technologies to transform other neglected resources into sustainable forms of energy. Rational Energies is in the energy transformation business. In 2012, Rational Energies pioneered a commercial pyrolysis process plant to convert waste plastic into crude oil. As they gained experience and knowledge about the process, the price per barrel for crude oil collapsed, leading us to recognize that a change of course was necessary. Today, Rational Energies has transformed their technology to utilize another waste stream, used motor oil (UMO), into Group I base oils, asphalt extender and distillate. Used motor oil is a major environmental challenge – one gallon of UMO can contaminate the drinking water for over one million people. With the technology and expertise at their disposal, Rational Energies continues to transform waste into valuable products.
